    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款刺激有趣的动作冒险游戏，你可以控制怪物进行战斗。游戏有单人冒险，单人Roguelike，也可以2人决斗，5人组队冒险，5V5阵营战，20人大乱斗等！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏是俯视角战斗，战斗中会有很多的道具，当你通关关卡后，就可以使用这关打败的敌人来战斗了。你需要小心场景中的各种机关！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高难度，爽快的战斗体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/d60bd8e4aceaedd214be5cb20936d410.poster.avif?t=1768816351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/d60bd8e4aceaedd214be5cb20936d410.webm?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/d60bd8e4aceaedd214be5cb20936d410.mp4?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组队闯关</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合作战斗，紧张刺激</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/cb19fc84e15a9d81a2160627c69e2485.poster.avif?t=1768816351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/cb19fc84e15a9d81a2160627c69e2485.webm?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/cb19fc84e15a9d81a2160627c69e2485.mp4?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >联机对战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4种联机玩法，等你体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/d76a9db14e0d55940acd24e4e406d768.poster.avif?t=1768816351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/d76a9db14e0d55940acd24e4e406d768.webm?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/d76a9db14e0d55940acd24e4e406d768.mp4?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/818a3627c7fd9383b4f0708f9ed2b35c.poster.avif?t=1768816351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/818a3627c7fd9383b4f0708f9ed2b35c.webm?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/818a3627c7fd9383b4f0708f9ed2b35c.mp4?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/19f6fd2a8a68838753d4f32dbd1f59ab.poster.avif?t=1768816351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/19f6fd2a8a68838753d4f32dbd1f59ab.webm?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/19f6fd2a8a68838753d4f32dbd1f59ab.mp4?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人对战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多人对战更加精彩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/8f610f69fa5a3ce5cbf74868eea5bddc.poster.avif?t=1768816351\" width=640 heig